latestIgtvVideos.title: TEDx Talk: Connect the dots turns one!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I have always believed in the power little victories and how we respond to them. Today is a special moment and I can’t help but look back at my journey as a creator in the past 8 years. I want to thank you all for helping my art and my voice reach it’s true potential. 

To my most loving Instagram family, here’s to so many more milestones together. We will together inspire and get inspired in this journey. I dedicate this precious moment to my 25k family.

latestIgtvVideos.title: A fun filled Instagram workshop with @tripotocommunity
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Smart businesses and brands know how important good instagram layouts are to create a successful first impression. 👀Whether you are a new Instagram user or a seasoned pro, a well thought out Instagram strategy can help you reach the right kind of people. 🗣

💡In this workshop, I will help you get creative with your Instagram feed in your own unique way. 

📝 Register for the workshop using the link in my bio.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Changing my feed after 1.5 years
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The end of your spine, the tail bone, was actually a tail. The appendix used to have a purpose and now it’s a rudimentary organ. Evolution always tells a story of what we leave behind and how little we can do without. 

Although a difficult choice to make, we always end up evolving. Changing my feed is a step towards evolving my creative expression and the manner in which I use this space to connect with you guys. Let’s make space for newer and better things to come our way. Thanks for sticking by me through it all, thank you my Instagram family, I couldn’t have asked for a better support system ❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Cutlery conversations
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The spork serves a noble cause.
Offering to hold, but with a claw. 
Each piece of cutlery in my house comes with its own history, scars, dents and purpose. 
Cutlery is funny, especially on a Thursday afternoon.

Shot and edited by yours truly. 
Music : RED by Rob Simonsen

latestIgtvVideos.title: 🔥Nuclear noodles challenge with #UnpauseWithKoovs
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
⚠️ not for the faint hearted ⚠️ House work, office work, nap, repeat. The past few days have been unusual as compared to the normal. But the one thing that brings me back to reality is my two special friends @bambrawrr and @subtle.strength ❤️. I am trying to pick up video editing as a skill this quarantine and have edited this video of our ⚠️ DEATHLY NUCLEAR NOODLES CHALLENGE ⚠️ I am unpausing and trying to keep my mind sane by learning. How are you Unpausing this quarantine? @koovsfashion #unpausewithkoovs
#nuclearnoodles #firenoodles #firenoodleschallenge
